review_text: Just for walk and play with your baby
Always filled with kids they deffenetly have fun there.
Very clean and beautiful park. I love spending time there with my friends and family.

(Translated by Google) Park completely restored in summer 2019. Children's games and cement table tennis table in the center.
Since June 2020, the park has been open despite COVID-19 by respecting the basic instructions.
Open 7 days a week from 7am to 11pm.
No dogs allowed.
Easy parking.

(Original)
Parc complètement restauré à l'été 2019. Jeux pour enfants et table de ping-pong en ciment au centre.
Depuis juin 2020, le parc est ouvert malgré la COVID-19 en respectant les consignes de base.
Ouvert 7j/7 de 7am à 11pm.
Chiens interdits.
Stationnement facile.
